#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="54"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa82"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.2.73"
msgid ""
"Upasampanno upasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo hīnena "
"hīnaṃ vadeti, oṭṭhaṃ meṇḍaṃ goṇaṃ gadrabhaṃ tiracchānagataṃ nerayikaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"If one who is fully ordained, wishing to revile, wishing to insult, wishing "
"to humiliate another who is fully ordained, says what is low to one who is "
"low—a camel/a ram/an ox/a donkey/an animal/one bound for hell—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.2.74"
msgid ""
"“oṭṭhosi, meṇḍosi, goṇosi, gadrabhosi, tiracchānagatosi, nerayikosi, natthi "
"tuyhaṃ sugati, duggati yeva tuyhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, "
"vācāya pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"saying, “You’re a camel/you’re a ram/you’re an ox/you’re a donkey/you’re an "
"animal/you’re not going to a good destination/you can only expect a bad "
"destination,” then for every statement, he commits an offense entailing "
"confession."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="55"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa83"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.2.75"
msgid ""
"Upasampanno upasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo hīnena "
"ukkaṭṭhaṃ vadeti, paṇḍitaṃ byattaṃ medhāviṃ bahussutaṃ dhammakathikaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"If one who is fully ordained, wishing to revile, wishing to insult, wishing "
"to humiliate another who is fully ordained, says what is low to one who is "
"high—one who is wise/one who is competent/one who is intelligent/one who is "
"learned/one who is an expounder of the Teaching—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.2.76"
msgid ""
"“oṭṭhosi, meṇḍosi, goṇosi, gadrabhosi, tiracchānagatosi, nerayikosi, natthi "
"tuyhaṃ sugati, duggatiyeva tuyhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, "
"vācāya pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
