#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="58"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-pc.2.2.3"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa86"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.1"
msgid ""
"Upasampanno upasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo evaṃ "
"vadeti, “santi idhekacce caṇḍālā venā nesādā rathakārā pukkusā”ti bhaṇati, "
"āpatti vācāya, vācāya dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If one who is fully ordained, wishing to revile, wishing to insult, wishing "
"to humiliate another who is fully ordained, says this, “There are outcasts/"
"bamboo workers/hunters/chariot-makers/waste-removers, right here,” then for "
"every statement, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="59"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa87"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.2"
msgid ""
"Upasampanno upasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo evaṃ "
"vadeti, “santi idhekacce khattiyā, brāhmaṇā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, "
"vācāya dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If one who is fully ordained, wishing to revile, wishing to insult, wishing "
"to humiliate another who is fully ordained, says this, “There are "
"aristocrats/brahmins, right here,” then for every statement, he commits an "
"offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="60"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.10"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa88"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.3"
msgid ""
"Upasampanno upasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo evaṃ "
"vadeti, “santi idhekacce avakaṇṇakā javakaṇṇakā dhaniṭṭhakā saviṭṭhakā "
"kulavaḍḍhakā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr ""
"If one who is fully ordained, wishing to revile, wishing to insult, wishing "
"to humiliate another who is fully ordained, says this, “There are "
"Avakaṇṇakas/Javakaṇṇakas/Dhaniṭṭhakas/Saviṭṭhakas/Kulavaḍḍhakas, right here” "
"…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.4"
msgid ""
"“Santi idhekacce buddharakkhitā dhammarakkhitā saṃgharakkhitā”ti bhaṇati … "
"pe …."
msgstr ""
"“There are Buddharakkhitas/Dhammarakkhitas/Sangharakkhitas, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.5"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce kosiyā bhāradvājā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "“There are Kosiyas/Bhāradvājas, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.6"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce gotamā moggallānā kaccānā vāsiṭṭhā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "“There are Gotamas/Moggallānas/Kaccānas/Vāsiṭṭhas, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.7"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce koṭṭhakā pupphachaḍḍakā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "“There are carpenters/waste-removers, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.8"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce kassakā vāṇijā gorakkhā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "“There are farmers/traders/cattle-keepers, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.9"
msgid ""
"“Santi idhekacce naḷakārā kumbhakārā pesakārā cammakārā nahāpitā”ti bhaṇati …"
" pe …."
msgstr ""
"“There are reed-workers/potters/weavers/leather-workers/hairdressers, right "
"here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.10"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce muddikā gaṇakā lekhakā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "“There are calculators/accountants/scribes, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.11"
msgid ""
"“Santi idhekacce kuṭṭhikā gaṇḍikā kilāsikā sosikā apamārikā”ti bhaṇati … pe "
"…."
msgstr ""
"“There are lepers/ones with boils/ones with tuberculosis/epileptics, right "
"here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.12"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce madhumehikā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "“There are diabetics right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.13"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce atidīghā atirassā atikaṇhā accodātā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“There are some who are too tall/some who are too short/some who are too "
"dark/some who are too fair, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.14"
msgid ""
"“Santi idhekacce nātidīghā nātirassā nātikaṇhā nāccodātā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“There are some who are not too tall/some who are not too short/some who are "
"not too dark/some who are not too fair, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.15"
msgid ""
"“Santi idhekacce rāgapariyuṭṭhitā dosapariyuṭṭhitā mohapariyuṭṭhitā”ti "
"bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“There are some who are full of sensual desire/some who are full of ill-will/"
"some who are full of confusion, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.16"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce vītarāgā vītadosā vītamohā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr ""
"“There are some without sensual desire/some without ill-will/some without "
"confusion, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.17"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce pārājikaṃ ajjhāpannā … pe …."
msgstr "“There are some who have committed an offense entailing expulsion/ … /"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.18"
msgid "dubbhāsitaṃ ajjhāpannā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "some who have committed an offense of bad speech, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.19"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce sotāpannā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "“There are stream-enterers right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.20"
msgid ""
"“Santi idhekacce oṭṭhā meṇḍā goṇā gadrabhā tiracchānagatā nerayikā, natthi "
"tesaṃ sugati, duggatiyeva tesaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, vācāya "
"dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"“There are camels/rams/oxen/donkeys/animals/those bound for hell/those who "
"are not going to a good destination/those who can only expect a bad "
"destination, right here,” then for every statement, he commits an offense of "
"wrong conduct."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="61"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa89"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.3.21"
msgid ""
"Upasampanno upasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo evaṃ "
"vadeti, “santi idhekacce paṇḍitā byattā, medhāvī bahussutā dhammakathikā, "
"natthi tesaṃ duggati, sugatiyeva tesaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, "
"vācāya dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If one who is fully ordained, wishing to revile, wishing to insult, wishing "
"to humiliate another who is fully ordained, says this, “There are wise ones/"
"competent ones/intelligent ones/learned ones/expounders of the Teaching/"
"those who are not going to a bad destination/those who can only expect a "
"good destination, right here,” then for every statement, he commits an "
"offense of wrong conduct."

