msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.4.1"
msgid ""
"Upasampanno upasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo evaṃ "
"vadeti, “ye nūna caṇḍālā venā nesādā rathakārā pukkusā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti "
